{"unitId":"KHS.af58bef5.main.a.DEF.00","term":"ア","termKey":"a","type":"DEF","quote":"无にして有也。五十連の惣名也。天也。海也。吾也。自然也。○也。","paraphrase":"アは“無にして有”の基底で、五十連の総名として置かれる。","sourceRef":"doc=NOTION:PAGE:af58bef540844ff59f19775177c8f3e8 pdfPage=415","tags":{"truth_axis":["center","manifestation"],"role_hint":["definition","evidence"],"kanagi_phase":["NAME"],"domain":["KHS"],"confidence":"primary","language":"ja","needs_evidence":false}}
{"unitId":"KHS.af58bef5.main.a.LAW.01","term":"ア","termKey":"a","type":"LAW","quote":"アは空水の水灵にして、ア行喉音也…五音の本也と云。","paraphrase":"アは空中の水灵であり、喉音として五音の基底に置かれる。","sourceRef":"doc=NOTION:PAGE:af58bef540844ff59f19775177c8f3e8 pdfPage=415","tags":{"truth_axis":["correspondence","order"],"role_hint":["definition"],"kanagi_phase":["NAME"],"domain":["KHS"],"confidence":"primary","language":"ja","needs_evidence":false}}
{"unitId":"KHS.af58bef5.main.ame.LAW.02","term":"アメ","termKey":"ame","type":"LAW","quote":"アは空中の水灵にして、メは回る義なり。空中の水の回るをアメと云。","paraphrase":"天（アメ）は空中水の回転（循環）として定義される。","sourceRef":"doc=NOTION:PAGE:af58bef540844ff59f19775177c8f3e8 pdfPage=415","tags":{"truth_axis":["cycle"],"role_hint":["definition"],"kanagi_phase":["NAME"],"domain":["KHS"],"confidence":"primary","language":"ja","needs_evidence":false}}
