{"unitId":"KHS.eed52861.main.iki.DEF.00","term":"水火","termKey":"iki","type":"DEF","quote":"動く物は水にして、動かしむる物は火なり。火の為に水動されて、始めて形を現して昇る。","paraphrase":"水=動、火=動因。形=顕現。","sourceRef":"doc=NOTION:PAGE:eed52861641d4d32ac88f3755c4c7a89 pdfPage=479","tags":{"truth_axis":["polarity","manifestation"],"role_hint":["definition"],"kanagi_phase":["NAME"],"domain":["KHS"],"confidence":"primary","language":"ja","needs_evidence":false}}
